    "body": "Object oriented. Create figure and axis references and manipute them. \n\n``` python\n%matplotlib inline\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nfig, ax = plt.subplots(1,1)\nfig.set_figwidth(7)\nfig.set_figheight(11)\nax.plot(range(10))\n```\n"
